<br>
And they would be, but not in every single circumstance, which is what you feel must be the case. Would it be useful on the vast majority of mobs in the elemental planes? Yes, it would. Are there are a few mobs that it wouldn't be useful on? Yup. Does the fact that there are some mobs it wouldn't be useful on somehow make it not useful at all? Nope. A better question would be, are there mobs that it would be useful on that your other pets are not useful on?  <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=4380">Qaman</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
