° Mighty, Hydro, Coirnav Ring<br>
° useless against Wise, Ofo<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>PoAir:</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Air&amp;Water pets beat the Fire Pet in this scenario (Damage). In fact the Air Pet Stun effect is a huge advantage over the other 2 pets.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>PoEarth:</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
As long as the AE spells are removed the Fire Pet would be an option, but the Air Pet wins again due to its Stun Effect which is much more valuable than silly nukes.<br>
<br>
<br>
Keep in mind, i am assuming the pet still has a limited mana pool and regular casting rules apply (recast time) and it has no immunities against any type of AE. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=3300" target="top">Sage Cyricus Bloodbane</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
